Enum BuiltInType

All Implemented Interfaces:

public enum BuiltInType
extends java.lang.Enum<BuiltInType>

EXI has a list built-in EXI datatype representations used for representing content items in EXI stream (see http://www.w3.org/TR/exi/#encodingDatatypes).

Additionally some built-in types are augmented with information necessary for machine processing (e.g., number of bits).

Version:
0.7
Author:
Daniel.Peintner.EXT@siemens.com, Joerg.Heuer@siemens.com
